snippet.title: Organic Panic Gameplay Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
https://www.playstation.com/en-us/games/organic-panic-ps4/

Fruits and veggies battle meats and cheeses in the first physics action platformer built with the DAFT (Destructibnle And Fluid Dynamics) engine. https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PygLHbxhmeg&feature=youtu.be - Over 200 levels of fluids and destrucibility featuring lots of game modes and Coop and Versus play too.
